{"lemma":"شافِعِ","slug":"شافِعِ","root":"ش.ف.ع","root_slug":"ش-ف-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ف-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شافِع","root":"شفع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22645"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%90%D8%B9%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22645","headword_ar":"شَافِعٌ","root":"$fE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of 1, q. v. ―         -b2-  Hence], applied to a she-camel, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having a young one in her belly and another following her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Sh, S, Mgh, K, TA:) or applied in this sense to a ewe or she-goat: (K:) or, thus applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having her young one with her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, S, Mgh:) thus called because her young one has made her to be one of a pair [with it], or because she has made it to be one of a pair [with her]: (A'Obeyd, S, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afuwEN","text_ar":"شَفُوعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", thus applied, signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAfiEN","text_ar":"شَافِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi $aApu Al$~aAfiEi","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ شَاةُ الشَّافِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SalaApu","text_ar":"صَلَاةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^uwlaY","text_ar":"الاُولَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masojidu AljaAmiEi","text_ar":"مَسْجِدُ الجَامِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A he-goat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,) himself: (O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a ram:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as, when he impregnates, impregnates with twins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN $aAfiEapN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ شَافِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that makes a thing to appear a pair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that sees doubly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yuEaAdiyniY walahu $aAfiEN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يُعَادِينِى وَلَهُ شَافِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one treats me with enmity, and has one who aids him to do so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b6-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afiyEN","text_ar":"شَفِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$af~aEN","text_ar":"مُشَفَّعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Fr","Sh","S","Mgh","K","TA","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}